# game-state-model

The game state model tracks and manages the complete state of a Spades card game through the following key components:

## Core State Components (src/lib/store.ts)

### Player State
- Current position/seat assignments 
- Team affiliations (North-South vs East-West)
- Individual bid amounts
- Tricks won per player
- Hand contents

### Team State
- Combined team bids
- Accumulated trick counts
- Running score totals
- Bag (overtrick) tracking
- Special bid states (nil/blind nil)

### Round State
- Active player turn tracking
- Current trick cards
- Lead suit requirements
- Spades broken status
- Trick history

### Score Tracking (src/lib/game/scoring.ts)
- Bid fulfillment tracking
- Nil/blind nil bonus/penalty calculation
- Bag accumulation and penalties
- Team score aggregation
- Win condition validation (500 points)

### Game Progression
- Turn sequencing
- Round completion logic
- Game completion detection
- Winner determination

